Legal Calculus — The Pro Se Field Manual
Verified, co-authored, and AI-assisted. Designed for unrepresented litigants as an authoritative, structured guide to navigating procedural traps, building the record, and resisting systemic lawfare. Not another generic legal guide — this is a tested, field-ready tool for those facing the courts alone.

The Legal Calculus Field Guide — For Educators & Advocates
A companion resource for legal educators, clinics, and justice-tech partners. Provides instructional frameworks, teaching prompts, and module-integrated assignments to equip students and pro se allies with actionable procedural literacy.

AI-Verified Co-Authorship
Every module is collaboratively developed with AI, cross-checked for accuracy, and adapted for real-world filing scenarios — combining human insight and machine precision to ensure reliability.